{"tid":807152,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[頹po]失咗戀先知點解煙咁難食都有人食，酒咁難飲都有人飲🤕","createTime":"2018-09-05T09:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T11:13:19.000Z","uid":154872,"like":7,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"73dbc11a6314ed0ed66d4091a99ad1b33d7a3134","tid":807152,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T09:52:46.000Z","msg":"😢😢😢<br />\n一齊咗成年幾<br />\n點解可以話分就分，咁狠心咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前生活一向好健康做開運動又早訓<br />\n好有規律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 煙酒都未試過<br />\n<br />\n尋晚自己落7仔<br />\n買咗包煙(求其話要包萬寶路, 佢問我要咩萬我都唔識, 求其要包紅白色哥隻)<br />\n買咗支black label<br />\n返屋企<br />\n開包煙一食<br />\n咳到我仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我都照忍住入肺<br />\n因為我喺煙嘅味道我同佢中學一齊做體檢哥陣嘅青澀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開支酒飲<br />\n飲冇幾耐我就衝咗入廁所嘔<br />\n諗返起佢以前知我身體差易暈所以每次都會入廁所到等我<br />\n<br />\n我終於知點解煙酒咁難入口都咁多人對佢地有依賴<br />\n<br />\n我真係好掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇人明<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29896eb7fdd4db824d521710548ae83fc773d54e","tid":807152,"uid":124667,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T09:56:41.000Z","msg":"食煙飲酒有鬼用 ， 用d錢call g 算啦"},{"pid":"1d535d131e68ee444f0592d535624ccb819b7f08","tid":807152,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29896eb7fdd4db824d521710548ae83fc773d54e","tid":807152,"uid":124667,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T09:56:41.000Z","msg":"食煙飲酒有鬼用 ， 用d錢call g 算啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T10:02:11.000Z","msg":"call g污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4da4c65024a2720d04c5a93bf88eb967fdb41b4","tid":807152,"uid":33059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T10:03:11.000Z","msg":"試埋屎未？"},{"pid":"da207d73bcf941112c2cafafeaf5df5